"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-celebrity-news-1933029-bbc-olympics-Andrea-Spendolini-Sirieix-diving\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"BBC Olympicsviewers have slammed an interviewer who spoke to Team GB diver Andrea Spendolini-Sirieix following her missing a chance to claim another medal.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 5, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9970476563686118, \"rank\": 0.0029399675164319267, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 77, \"end\": 102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrea_Spendolini-Sirieix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrea Spendolini-Sirieix\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrea_Spendolini-Sirieix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrea_Spendolini-Sirieix\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an interviewer\", \"from\": 33, \"to\": 47}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 123, \"to\": 131}, {\"ngram\": \"another medal\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 154}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 19-year old was visibly upset after she finished sixth in the women's 10m platform final on Tuesday and during her interview she opened up about her mental health battles.\", \"from\": 159, \"to\": 334, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the women's 10m\", \"from\": 221, \"to\": 236}, {\"ngram\": \"platform\", \"from\": 237, \"to\": 245}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 255, \"to\": 262}, {\"ngram\": \"her interview\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 287}, {\"ngram\": \"her mental health battles\", \"from\": 308, \"to\": 333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Andrea was so emotional that she could barely speak, catching her breath with every word as she broke down in tears.\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Andrea\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 342}, {\"ngram\": \"her breath\", \"from\": 398, \"to\": 408}, {\"ngram\": \"every word\", \"from\": 414, \"to\": 424}, {\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Qasa Alom asked her: \\\"Andrea, it wasn't meant to be in the end.\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 453, \"end\": 457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kassi_(wife_of_Suleyman_of_Mali)\", \"score\": 0.9999999992801349, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Qasa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kassi_(wife_of_Suleyman_of_Mali)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kassi_(wife_of_Suleyman_of_Mali)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You finished seventh last time, sixth this time and I can just see how emotional you were as you finished your final dive.\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 641, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your final dive\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 640}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just tell us how you are feeling.\\\"\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 676, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 654}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The diver replied: \\\"Obviously, it wasn't the result that I wanted but I am not even upset with the competition, I mean the girls dove amazing, they did better than me today and it is because they worked really hard.\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 893, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The diver\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 687}, {\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 729}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 788}, {\"ngram\": \"the girls\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 806}]}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE:Keely Hodgkinson's 'worst part' of 800m gold speaks volumes about character \\\"And yeah, as you said it wasn't meant to be and, I am not even... Genuinely, I am not trying to be macho or anything, I am not upset with my performance, three years ago I did not even want to be alive.\\\"\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 1188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 905, \"end\": 921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"800m\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 944}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 949}, {\"ngram\": \"volumes\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 964}, {\"ngram\": \"character\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 980}, {\"ngram\": \"my performance\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1134}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alom continued to question Andrea about her performance, asking her for \\\"one moment\\\" and noted that everyone was proud of her before finally allowing her to go and see her family.\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alom\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1194}, {\"ngram\": \"Andrea\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1223}, {\"ngram\": \"her performance\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1245}, {\"ngram\": \"one moment\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1273}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1298}, {\"ngram\": \"her family\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Viewers have been left fuming over the interview, with many taking to social media to slam Alom for his \\\"cruel\\\" lack of regard for Andrea's emotional state.\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1527, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Viewers\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1378}, {\"ngram\": \"the interview\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1419}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1453}, {\"ngram\": \"Alom\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1466}, {\"ngram\": \"his \\\"cruel\\\" lack\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1487}, {\"ngram\": \"regard\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1497}, {\"ngram\": \"Andrea's emotional st